            <div class="title">
                First Lord Of The Admiralty (Speech)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1939-04-06/debates/a127a93e-33ad-4dd1-8cf0-7dfd829fdee1/PotteryAndEarthenwareIndustry" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
